{"tid":2478526,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜丹尼爾自爆曾遭校園霸凌 被打兼搶錢：好像因長相問題","createTime":"2021-04-07T06:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T06:28:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd3298ee905004a45d991ec68faff451b9c5e66","tid":2478526,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b5VGBjDlqHceaDgsMWGIOnoykzE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MWYX45R36FFLZGP5TDFGNHSYBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb5VGBjDlqHceaDgsMWGIOnoykzE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMWYX45R36FFLZGP5TDFGNHSYBI.jpg&h=72f46971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因參加韓國選秀節目《PRODUCE 101》第二季獲冠軍的24歲姜丹尼爾，他曾陷合約問題跟前事務所對簿公堂、又曾被爆與女團TWICE隊長志效拍拖等是非，令他因而患上抑鬱症、恐慌障礙並停工數月。<br />\n<br />\n加害者當遊戲<br />\n而姜丹尼爾昨日亮相KBS的節目《屋塔房的問題兒童們》，他自爆亦曾是校園暴力的受害者，他說：「小學時轉學了幾次，因為受到了很多欺負。 不知道被孤立的理由，好像是對我長相不太滿意。小學四五年級時，錢也會被哥哥們搶走，發現我時又會被打。對於加害者來說，這只是一種遊戲而已。」<br />\n<br />\n母親是治癒良藥<br />\n姜丹尼爾在節目內亦有提及母親，又指自己在練習生時期，多虧了母親，令他得到了治癒，透露母親當時每周打一次電話給自己，令他充滿很大的力量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bIQKg7ztekfu6krKf3lIoP6g2HQ=/802x2232/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XGIPILS3BVHEJG5TNERKQA5LMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbIQKg7ztekfu6krKf3lIoP6g2HQ%3D%2F802x2232%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXGIPILS3BVHEJG5TNERKQA5LMA.jpg&h=3074a1dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210407/PJAKB53VDVDC5HBKR2HUF76ELY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210407%2FPJAKB53VDVDC5HBKR2HUF76ELY%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtPLVWyXx